text: Kyzyl-Tash () is a rural locality (a village) in Gafurovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 26 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Tuymazy, 25 km from Duslyk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kyzyl-Tash, Republic of Bashkortostan
